author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-CS Communication & Systemes H1 net income group share rises to 0.4 mln euros
text:
Sept 4 CS Communication & Systemes SA :
* H1 net income group share 0.4 million euros ($445,720.00)versus 0.3 million euros previous year
* H1 operating income 1.7 million euros versus 2.7 million euros previous year
* H1 revenue 83.0 million euros versus 82.4 million euros year ago Source text: bit.ly/1FnJn3I Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8974 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom:)
